Sentencas: The implementation of a PC-based quality control system for the manufacturing of anode-supported solid oxide fuel cells (SOFCs) is a prerequisite for achieving reproducibility and high quality of the cells.
Titulo: Processing and quality control of planar SOFC components

Sentencas: To reach that goal a broad database for each manufacturing step including materials and processes is needed.
Titulo: Processing and quality control of planar SOFC components

Sentencas: This database is generated on the basis of the well developed manufacturing route of the Julich planar SOFC.
Titulo: Processing and quality control of planar SOFC components
